\SE[94]Haa... Haa... I never thought I would end up saving a
life... \SE[74]

\SE[33]Cough...! I-I'm alright... \SE[91]I'm sorry, it seems
like you saved me somehow...

\SE[75]I must say, I've been too kind- hearted...
\!\SE[2]So, do you know where we are?

\SE[75] (...Well, that's true. I asked a meaningless
question.)
(Ugh... I guess I'll just make something up.)

\SE[2]I don't know much about it either... But I think it's
probably an abandoned underground waterway that hasn't been
used since before the founding of Ulyssean... \SE[3]

\SE[2]Wow... I never knew there was a place like this
beneath such a splendid city...

\SE[2]It seems like the previous country was in ruins...
Well, that's beside the point. \SE[3]Because it's that kind
of place, I think monsters will appear.

\SM[nod]\SE[0]Ah, yeah. \SE[16]I've been training recently,
so I should be fine even if it's a little tough.

\SE[4]Oh, really...? \!\SE[0]Well then, let's try to find an
exit since I think there should be one.
\SE[2]Got it! I'm Laura. \SE[2]Um... and you are?

\SE[2]My name? \!\SE[3]Don't worry about it. I'm not someone
worth introducing myself.

\SE[75] (Well, this turned into an unexpected development. I
wonder what will happen...)
